## Model

![image-20230110145320107](../AppData/Roaming/Typora/typora-user-images/image-20230110145320107.png)

driven：
$$
\begin{array}{c}
m_{w} \ddot{x}=N_{f}-N \\
I_{w} \frac{\ddot{x}}{R}=T-N_{f} R
\end{array}
$$
leg：
$$
\begin{array}{c}
N-N_{M}=m_{p} \frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial t^{2}}(x+L \sin \theta) \\
P-P_{M}-m_{p} g=m_{p} \frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial t^{2}}(L \cos \theta) \\
I_{p} \ddot{\theta}=\left(P L+P_{M} L_{M}\right) \sin \theta-\left(N L+N_{M} L_{M}\right) \cos \theta-T+T_{p}
\end{array}
$$
body：
$$
\begin{array}{c}
N_{M}=M \frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial t^{2}}\left(x+\left(L+L_{M}\right) \sin \theta-l \sin \phi\right) \\
P_{M}-M g=M \frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial t^{2}}\left(\left(L+L_{M}\right) \cos \theta+l \cos \phi\right) \\
I_{M} \ddot{\phi}=T_{p}+N_{M} l \cos \phi+P_{M} l \sin \phi
\end{array}
$$


linearization:
$$
\boldsymbol{A}=\frac{\partial f}{\partial \boldsymbol{x}}(\overline{\boldsymbol{x}}, \overline{\boldsymbol{u}}), \quad \boldsymbol{B}=\frac{\partial f}{\partial \boldsymbol{u}}(\overline{\boldsymbol{x}}, \overline{\boldsymbol{u}})
$$

- [x] 平衡点处线性化
- [ ] 根据腿长变化求取增益，用多项式拟合
- [ ] 在每个工作点线性化求增益，用多项式拟合（二维）
- [ ] 实时线性化+MPC。运算平台选型

## VMC

![image-20230110145608194](../AppData/Roaming/Typora/typora-user-images/image-20230110145608194.png)
$$
\boldsymbol{x}=\left[\begin{array}{ll}
L_{0} & \phi_{0}
\end{array}\right]^{T}, \boldsymbol{q}=\left[\begin{array}{ll}
\phi_{1} & \phi_{4}
\end{array}\right]^{T}
$$

$$
\begin{aligned}
\delta L_{0} & =\frac{\partial f_{1}}{\partial \phi_{1}} \delta \phi_{1}+\frac{\partial f_{1}}{\partial \phi_{4}} \delta \phi_{4} \\
\delta \phi_{0} & =\frac{\partial f_{2}}{\partial \phi_{1}} \delta \phi_{1}+\frac{\partial f_{2}}{\partial \phi_{4}}  \delta \phi_{4}
\end{aligned} \tag{jacobi}
$$

$$
\delta \boldsymbol{x}=\boldsymbol{J} \delta \boldsymbol{q} \tag{1}
$$

$$
T=[T_1\quad T_2]^T,F=[F \quad T_d]^T
$$

$$
\boldsymbol{T}^{\mathrm{T}} \delta \boldsymbol{q}+(-\boldsymbol{F})^{\mathrm{T}} \delta \boldsymbol{x}=0 \tag{2}
$$

$$
\boldsymbol{T}=\boldsymbol{J}^{T} \boldsymbol{F}
$$
